title: introNPC
position: -10,-9
---
Hey there Buddy.
Nice to see you. Not many people come around these parts.
I heard you're looking for something like the thing I have here.
I'd be happy to give it to you... for a price!
Find me another object that looks like this, and we can make a trade.
Sound good?
<<set $firstVisit = true>>
    ->Yes!
        <<jump accepted>>
    ->Nah.
        <<jump denied>>
===
title: accepted
