        <<_collectItem item>>
        <<set $doneQuest = true>>
        <<else>>
        Please don't joke with me.
        Go get my shit.
        <<endif>>
    ->Nope.
        Ok... then... go get it, I guess?
<<else>>
Did you rethink my offer?
    ->Yeah.
        <<jump accepted>>
    ->No.
        <<jump denied>>
<<endif>>
<<else>>
Hey! Good to see you, partner.
